column16: Buster Posey walks.   Joe Panik to 2nd.

Rougned Odor strikes out on a foul tip.

Carlos Corporan flies out to right fielder George Springer.
Carlos Peguero strikes out swinging, catcher Jason Castro to first baseman Chris Carter.
